{
  "text": "The approximate frequency given in Eq. (33) is the same that the frequency obtained by applying the method proposed by Wu and Lim [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] in which they combine the harmonic balance method and linearization of nonlinear oscillation equation (see Appendix II).",
